This paper discusses software fault prediction models and techniques, which are related to software engineering (cs.SE). The use of bandit algorithms to address external validity is a machine learning approach, which falls under categories such as cs.LG (machine learning) and cs.AI (artificial intelligence). The paper also discusses the evaluation of prediction models, which is related to computer security (cs.CR) and software testing (cs.SI).
